🛠️ Installation

<details>
<summary><b>📥 Click to Expand Installation Guide</b></summary>

Local Development

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/telegram-string-generator-bot.git
cd telegram-string-generator-bot

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# Activate virtual environment
# On Linux/Mac:
source venv/bin/activate
# On Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Create environment file
cp .env.example .env

# Edit .env with your credentials
nano .env

# Run the bot
python main.py
```

Docker Installation

```bash
# Build Docker image
docker build -t telegram-string-bot .

# Run container
docker run -d \
  --name telegram-bot \
  -p 5000:5000 \
  --env-file .env \
  telegram-string-bot

# Check logs
docker logs -f telegram-bot
```

</details>

