🐛 Troubleshooting

<details>
<summary><b>🔧 Click for Common Issues & Solutions</b></summary>

Issue 1: Bot Not Starting

```bash
❌ ERROR: BOT_TOKEN is required!
```

Solution: Set BOT_TOKEN in environment variables.

---

Issue 2: Admin Commands Not Working

```bash
⛔ You are not authorized to use this command.
```

Solution: Add your Telegram ID to ADMIN_IDS.

---

Issue 3: Rate Limit Exceeded

```bash
⚠️ Rate Limit Exceeded
```

Solution: Wait 5 minutes or increase RATE_LIMIT.

---

Issue 4: Invalid API Credentials

```bash
❌ Invalid API_ID or API_HASH
```

Solution: Get valid credentials from my.telegram.org.

---

Issue 5: Session Timeout

```bash
⏳ Session expired
```

Solution: Start again with /generate.

---

Issue 6: Flood Wait

```bash
⏳ Flood Wait: 30 seconds
```

Solution: Wait for the specified time before retrying.

</details>

